who successfully made the journey to baptism

00:51:38.462 --> 00:51:43.066 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and saw the joy and happiness
of that special day.

00:51:44.501 --> 00:51:46.503 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Before we close,

00:51:46.503 --> 00:51:50.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
let’s visit our brothers
and sisters in Angola.

00:51:50.640 --> 00:51:55.112 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Republic of Angola
is on the west coast of Africa.

00:51:55.112 --> 00:51:59.249 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is a beautiful
and geographically diverse land.

00:51:59.249 --> 00:52:04.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s home
to the breathtaking Kalandula Falls.

00:52:04.020 --> 00:52:07.991 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The ministry here
ranges from the city of Luanda,

00:52:07.991 --> 00:52:11.394 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
where the territory is worked every few days,

00:52:11.394 --> 00:52:15.065 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to rugged and remote areas accessible

00:52:15.065 --> 00:52:17.601 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
only by walking.

00:52:17.601 --> 00:52:19.669 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Angola’s population

00:52:19.669 --> 00:52:23.807 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of some 30 million people

00:52:23.807 --> 00:52:27.544 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
includes many indigenous tribes
and language groups.

00:52:29.379 --> 00:52:32.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
About 45 percent of the population

00:52:32.282 --> 00:52:35.819 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is under the age of 15.

00:52:35.819 --> 00:52:37.954 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Angola has been recovering

00:52:37.954 --> 00:52:42.792 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from a civil war that lasted 27 years.

00:52:42.792 --> 00:52:47.164 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Despite the challenges,
many are embracing the truth.

00:52:48.798 --> 00:52:50.800 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Angola is home

00:52:50.800 --> 00:52:54.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to more than 160,000
Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:52:55.338 --> 00:52:57.474 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They’re conducting

00:52:57.474 --> 00:53:01.478 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
over 720,000 Bible studies.

00:53:01.478 --> 00:53:04.614 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
An average of 25 people

00:53:04.614 --> 00:53:07.117 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are baptized every day,

00:53:07.117 --> 00:53:11.888 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
13 congregations are formed every month,

00:53:11.888 --> 00:53:13.557 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and an average

00:53:13.557 --> 00:53:18.128 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of 15 new circuits every year.

00:53:18.128 --> 00:53:23.033 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This has created
a tremendous need for places of worship.

00:53:23.033 --> 00:53:27.304 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Currently, more than 300 new Kingdom Halls

00:53:27.304 --> 00:53:30.941 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and 13 new Assembly Halls are needed.

00:53:30.941 --> 00:53:35.178 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is the Malueca Congregation in Luanda.

00:53:36.179 --> 00:53:39.516 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This beautiful Kingdom Hall
was recently completed

00:53:39.516 --> 00:53:43.887 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and is already used by five congregations.

00:53:43.887 --> 00:53:47.891 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our dear brothers and sisters in Angola

00:53:47.891 --> 00:53:50.560 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
send you their love and greetings.

00:53:53.163 --> 00:53:55.332 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And, brothers and sisters,

00:53:55.332 --> 00:53:58.702 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we love you all very much.

00:53:58.702 --> 00:54:01.938 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
From the World Headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:54:01.938 --> 00:54:05.175 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this is JW Broadcasting!

